                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#1v">f. 1v</locus>
                           <desc>: Recipe against one’s enemies (?). </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              ዮድ፡ ደዮን፡ ዋዋስ፡ ጠርቅዮስ፡ ዝብጥ፡ ሕሊናሆሙ፡ ለፀርየ፡
                              ወለፀላትየ[sic]፡…</q>

                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#2v">f. 2v-3r</locus>
                           <desc>Recipe against cancer (?). </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"> የሴት፡ ቀስት፡ አብላሊት፡…</q>
                           
                           <note> Different plants like asparagus, č̣at or cactus are mentioned.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#3r">f. 3r</locus>
                           <desc>Recipe against cancer. </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ቃል፡ ለነቀርሰ፡ መጅን፡ ዘሀጅን፡ ዋህ፡
                              እቅጅጅ፡…</q>

                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#47v">f. 47v-48r</locus>
                           <desc>ʾAsmat-prayer (?).</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ንጅን፡ ሸፈጅን፡ ተፈጅን፡ ዓይ፡ ነባሪኖ፡ ን፡ ፒፒካዳ፡
                              …</q>
                          
                           <note> It gives directives to recite the prayer 7 times a day for 7 days.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus target="#48r">f. 48r-49r</locus>
                           <desc>Recipe against illness (?).</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"> የአብላሊት፡ ስር፡ የሴት፡ ቀሰት፡ ጥፈረርያ፡ ሰር፡
                              የታቦት፡ አፈር፡ የገብያ፡ አፈር። ዲን፡ ሸንፋ፡ ነጭ፡ ሸንኩርተ፡ ዕፀ፡ ይወዲት። በሐዲስ፡ ጬርቅ፡ ዕስር።
                              ለራሽህ፡ መጠብጫ፡ የሰነት፡ ቅርፍት። ፯ቀን፡ በመዐር …</q>
                           <note> Written with two different pens (?). Mentioning the use of several
                              ingredients such as dust from the tabot (የታቦት፡ አፈር), garlic (ነጭ፡
                              ሸንኩርተ) or cactus (ቍልቋል). </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <locus target="#50r">f. 50r</locus>
                           <desc>Recipe against illness (?).</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">አብላሊት፡ ዕፀ፡ እስክንድር፡ ቀጋ። የቀንጦፋ፡ ተቀጽላ፡
                              …</q>
                           
                           <note> Written in a secondary, sloppy hand, on an extra piece of paper.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1"><desc>- Texts V and VI are written in compressed script.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e2"><desc>
                           Magic square or calendar (?), recent talismanic drawing in pencil: <locus target="#3v">3v</locus>, 49v.</desc></item>
                        <item xml:id="e3"><desc>The title of Text II, written in
